{"tid":2074734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"奶共Apple：將在中國下架數千款未獲批准的iPhone遊戲，嚴格遵守中國網遊法規","createTime":"2020-06-22T10:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T11:27:19.000Z","uid":48040,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd06de69e2ca8a9e558fff1c82315900e34cb34","tid":2074734,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"Bloomberg報導，蘋果將在中國下架數千款未獲批准的iPhone遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n日前GameLook微信公眾號消息稱，蘋果公司確認將嚴格遵守中國法律對遊戲產品的相關規定，並對在中國區運營的iOS平台遊戲進行嚴格的資質審核。從今年7月起、無版新遊戲將再無法通過蘋果審核和上架中國區AppStore。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/apple-set-to-nix-thousands-of-unlicensed-iphone-games-in-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-06-22%2Fapple-set-to-nix-thousands-of-unlicensed-iphone-games-in-china&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=b89916c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-06-22/apple-set-to-nix-thousands-of-unlicensed-iphone-games-in-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tech.sina.com.cn/digi/2020-06-22/doc-iirczymk8392411.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftech.sina.com.cn%2Fdigi%2F2020-06-22%2Fdoc-iirczymk8392411.shtml&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=b4ca23f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tech.sina.com.cn/digi/2020-06-22/doc-iirczymk8392411.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n訂閱人數達到一萬！多謝大家支持！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe7Q0NLD83eI&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=b20a8a54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI</a>"},{"pid":"79771c06874fd5dd1a8b3364ede673f10672e116","tid":2074734,"uid":48040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook奶到雪雪聲，最終都係難逃一劫"},{"pid":"6af0